      "locked": false,
      "text": "React\n    React is a js frontent library(angular is a framework)\n    its used to create single page applications and attractive ux\n\nReact features\n    single page application\n    virtual dom(Reconciliation)\n    declarative\n    Component Based Architecture\n    One way data binding\n\nHistory\n   Jorden Walke 2011 working facebook\n\n    2013-open source\n    2014-Used in instagram\n\n    latest version -> 19\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "React\n    React is a js frontent library(angular is a framework)\n    its used to create single page applications and attractive ux\n\nReact features\n    single page application\n    virtual dom(Reconciliation)\n    declarative\n    Component Based Architecture\n    One way data binding\n\nHistory\n   Jorden Walke 2011 working facebook\n\n    2013-open source\n    2014-Used in instagram\n\n    latest version -> 19\n",
