      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Single Page vs Multi-Page Application\n\n| Feature             | Single Page Application (SPA)      | Multi Page Application (MPA)           |\n| ------------------- | ---------------------------------- | -------------------------------------- |\n| Definition          | One HTML page, dynamically updated | Multiple HTML pages loaded from server |\n| Page Reload         | ❌ No full reload                   | ✅ Full page reload every request       |\n| Speed               | Fast after initial load            | Slower due to repeated reloads         |\n| Initial Load        | Slower (loads JS bundle)           | Faster per page                        |\n| Navigation          | Smooth (client-side routing)       | Traditional (server-side routing)      |\n| Rendering           | Client-side rendering              | Server-side rendering                  |\n| SEO                 | Harder (needs SSR/SSG)             | Easier (content from server)           |\n| User Experience     | App-like, seamless                 | Less smooth                            |\n| Backend Load        | Lower (fewer requests)             | Higher (many requests)                 |\n| Frontend Complexity | High                               | Moderate                               |\n| Examples            | React, Angular apps                | PHP, JSP websites                      |\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Single Page vs Multi-Page Application\n\n| Feature             | Single Page Application (SPA)      | Multi Page Application (MPA)           |\n| ------------------- | ---------------------------------- | -------------------------------------- |\n| Definition          | One HTML page, dynamically updated | Multiple HTML pages loaded from server |\n| Page Reload         | ❌ No full reload                   | ✅ Full page reload every request       |\n| Speed               | Fast after initial load            | Slower due to repeated reloads         |\n| Initial Load        | Slower (loads JS bundle)           | Faster per page                        |\n| Navigation          | Smooth (client-side routing)       | Traditional (server-side routing)      |\n| Rendering           | Client-side rendering              | Server-side rendering                  |\n| SEO                 | Harder (needs SSR/SSG)             | Easier (content from server)           |\n| User Experience     | App-like, seamless                 | Less smooth                            |\n| Backend Load        | Lower (fewer requests)             | Higher (many requests)                 |\n| Frontend Complexity | High                               | Moderate                               |\n| Examples            | React, Angular apps                | PHP, JSP websites                      |\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
